text: "It's Not Over" is a 2006 debut single by American rock band Daughtry. It is the leading single from their debut studio album Daughtry. It went to number 4 in the United States, number 128 in the United Kingdom, number 8 in New Zealand, number 9 in Canada, number 77 in Switzerland and number 22 in Australia. It was nominated for 2 Grammy Awards in 2008. ==Track listing== #"It's Not Over" #"It's Not Over" ==References== Category:2006 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Daughtry (band) songs
